{"word":"συρίζω","slug":"συρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συρίζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to play the</i> <el>σῦριγξ</el>, <i>to pipe</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>συρίζων ὑμεναίους</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to whistle, hiss</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>συρίζων φόνον</el> <i>hissing forth</i> murder, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to hiss</i> an actor, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>explodere</el>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}